      • FILTER_USER_ACTIVITY_STATISTICS_BY_DATE_TC

        public void FILTER_USER_ACTIVITY_STATISTICS_BY_DATE_TC()
                                                throws java.awt.AWTException,
                                                       java.lang.Exception
        Summary
        Filter User Activity Statistics by date
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        User should have administrator rights
        Steps
        1. Click on UserName on right upper corner of browser window
        2. Click on 'Reports'
        3. Navigate to 'User Activity Statistics'
        4. Enter Form Date
        5. Enter To Date
        6. Click on Search button
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify that data should be retrieved as per dates entered
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - Exception if file is not found
        java.awt.AWTException - Signals that an Abstract Window Toolkit exception has occurred
